empresa.p.1: We are dedicated to the production, processing and marketing of soybeans and wheat. We offer the controlled seed market of leading companies. In addition, we provide third-party processing service due to our extensive operational capacity.
empresa.p.2: As quality is our priority, we comply with the standards established by the National Seed Institute and by the different hatcheries we work with. We know that a good harvest starts with a good seed.Ks
empresa.p.3: We have a 4500 m2 covered processing plant and staff with extensive experience in the field. In addition, we add technology to our seeds through a Professional Seed Treatment Unit (PST).
mision.p.1: Generate and Market agricultural products and services, co-create associative projects, provide comprehensive advice, investment alternatives and services in a sustainable social way, environmentally and economically, in a framework of training and development of people, creating and strengthening links within the Network.
vision.p.1: We are an inclusive Agroindustrial Cooperative, we generate value and evolve together with associates and other members of the Network.
